dc_title_s: Program of All-Inclusive Care for the Elderly Regions, Wisconsin 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents program of all-inclusive care for the elderly region boundaries for Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset contains boundaries for the Program of All-Inclusive Care regions. The Program of All-Inclusive Care for the Elderly, also known as PACE, provides a full range of long-term care, health care, and prescription drugs to older people with chronic needs. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/familycare/pace.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/8cdcbf6e3c3242bd8d5222268567bf79_10?geometry=-103.702%2C42.041%2C-75.951%2C47.494
